安裝順序:
1. libucimf
2. jfbterm
3. ucimf-openvanilla
4. openvanilla-module-im???


手動開發的過程
所需工具:
• subversion
• autotools
	• automake
		• automake
		•  aclocal
	• autoconf
		• autoreconf
	• libtool
	• g++
	• make
• freetype
	• libfreetype6-dev
• libltdl3-dev
	• ltdl.h

包裝工具
• dpkg-dev
	• dpkg-buildpackage
• debhelper
• fakeroot


抓取最新的源始碼
svn checkout http://ucimf.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/ucimf ucimf
svn checkout 	http://openvanilla.googlecode.com/svn/trunk openvanilla

編譯
1.libucimf
 cd ${UCIMF_SRC}/libucimf/
 autoreconf -i
 ./configure && make && make install

2.ucimf-openvanilla

 cd ${UCIMF_SRC}/ucimf-openvanilla/
 autoreconf -i
 ./configure && make && make install

3.openvanilla

cd ${OV_SRC}/
make debian

